etz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article-live/.premium/israel-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-lebanon-gantz-kicks-off-u-s-visit/0000018e-0776-d822-a9ce-7ff77a760000</guid></item><item><title>副总统卡马拉·哈里斯对以色列自 10 月 7 日以来在加沙的行动提出美国最严厉的谴责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/vp-kamala-harris-offers-harshest-u-s-rebuke-of-israels-actions-in-gaza-since-october-7/0000018e-06a7-d5ee-a78e-36e7dbff0000</link><description>迄今为止，在以色列针对哈马斯的战争中，哈里斯一直被拜登政府视为“黑脸”，但她周日的言论是美国言论的一个转折点</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 23:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-04/ty-article/.premium/vp-kamala-harris-offers-harshest-u-s-rebuke-of-israels-actions-in-gaza-since-october-7/0000018e-06a7-d5ee-a78e-36e7dbff0000</guid></item><item><title>不是意识形态，而是个人：甘茨的美国之行凸显了对内塔尼亚胡的完全不信任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/not-ideological-personal-gantzs-u-s-visit-underscores-utter-distrust-in-netanyahu/0000018e-0606-d5ee-a78e-36c6523b0000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡得知甘茨成功抢了他的车后，总理有两个选择：第一个是向他表示祝贺，并向旅行者提供消息，以便转发给华盛顿和唐宁街 10 号。第二个是，嗯，发狂</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 20:59:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/not-ideological-personal-gantzs-u-s-visit-underscores-utter-distrust-in-netanyahu/0000018e-0606-d5ee-a78e-36c6523b0000</guid></item><item><title>经过10年的努力，加沙的一名巴勒斯坦妇女生下了双胞胎。以色列的袭击杀死了他们两人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/after-10-years-of-trying-a-woman-in-gaza-had-twins-an-israeli-strike-killed-them-both/0000018e-055c-d3bd-afce-b5dff6ca0000</link><description>据幸存者和当地卫生官员称，以色列袭击袭击了加沙南部拉法的一处房屋，造成 13 名家庭成员死亡，另有 9 人在废墟下失踪</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/after-10-years-of-trying-a-woman-in-gaza-had-twins-an-israeli-strike-killed-them-both/0000018e-055c-d3bd-afce-b5dff6ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名在加沙地带南部战斗中丧生的预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-reserves-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018e-0596-d5ee-a78e-35d678300000</link><description>中士。来自佩塔提克瓦的 33 岁丹尼斯·叶基莫夫 (Dennis Yekimov) 少校于周六在汗尤尼斯被杀。 “我再也见不到你了，只在照片里。”你是世界上最好的父亲，”他的小女儿哀悼道</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:50:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-reserves-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018e-0596-d5ee-a78e-35d678300000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯拒绝公布人质要求后，以色列抵制在开罗举行的加沙谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-boycotts-gaza-talks-in-cairo-after-hamas-rejects-demand-to-name-hostages/0000018e-05ba-df38-a98f-7fbe56e60000</link><description>以色列安全内阁的消息人士批评内塔尼亚胡要求获得在与哈马斯达成协议时释放的活着人质的完整名单。一位人士表示，“这不需要成为推进谈判的障碍”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-boycotts-gaza-talks-in-cairo-after-hamas-rejects-demand-to-name-hostages/0000018e-05ba-df38-a98f-7fbe56e60000</guid></item><item><title>正确阅读民意调查：大多数美国人支持以色列而不是哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-03/ty-article/.highlight/read-the-polls-properly-most-americans-back-israel-over-hamas/0000018e-0552-d5dd-abce-cf7ad9680000</link><description>如果以色列人没有在以色列的每个新闻周期中一次又一次地被告知，反以色列、支持哈马斯的情绪正在席卷美国，吓坏那里的犹太人和以色列人呢？</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 19:12:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-03/ty-article/.highlight/read-the-polls-properly-most-americans-back-israel-over-hamas/0000018e-0552-d5dd-abce-cf7ad9680000</guid></item><item><title>2500万年前的一次突变如何让人类失去了尾巴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-03/ty-article/how-a-single-mutation-25-million-years-ago-cost-humans-our-tails/0000018e-04ec-d5dd-abce-cfee635e0000</link><description>一项新的研究探讨了人类尾巴缺失背后的神秘遗传机制，一些人认为这可能是类人猿两足行走的关键</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 18:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-03/ty-article/how-a-single-mutation-25-million-years-ago-cost-humans-our-tails/0000018e-04ec-d5dd-abce-cfee635e0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 149 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-149/0000018e-0558-d5dd-abce-cf7a9a0e0000</link><description>在卡塔尔称哈马斯未能发送待释放俘虏名单后，以色列坚持派代表团前往开罗 ■ 哈马斯消息人士称，协议可能“在几天内达成” ■ 以色列国防军：对超过 115 名等待援助的加沙人死亡的初步调查发现，以色列军队并未袭击他们 ■ 以色列国家粮食安全委员会主席因加沙“极度饥饿”而呼吁停火 ■ 战争已持续 149 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 17:45:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-149/0000018e-0558-d5dd-abce-cf7a9a0e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方没有意识到加沙地带因饥饿而造成大规模死亡的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/the-israeli-military-doesnt-grasp-the-risk-of-mass-death-by-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-041f-dc7c-a3cf-4cffa3aa0000</link><description>针对等待援助卡车的巴勒斯坦人的枪击事件反映出他们对局势严重性的无知。尽管以色列无视人道主义组织的警告，但世界正在倾听</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 17:19:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/the-israeli-military-doesnt-grasp-the-risk-of-mass-death-by-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-041f-dc7c-a3cf-4cffa3aa0000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔镇压巴勒斯坦标志，以色列警方逮捕挥舞巴勒斯坦国旗的足球迷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-soccer-fan-waving-palestinian-flag-amid-crackdown-on-palestinian-emblems/0000018e-04ff-d6be-afff-44ff85670000</link><description>尽管极右翼国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Ita