t-20-thousand-children-classified-victims-of-terror-since-oct-7/0000018e-044f-d5c1-a98e-d44f02ee0000</guid></item><item><title>连续多雨天气后，数百只异常巨大的水母被冲上以色列海岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-unusually-large-jellyfish-wash-up-on-israels-shores-after-spate-of-rain/0000018e-03cf-def2-a98e-cfff35c00000</link><description>虽然夏季通常被认为是水母的高峰季节，但冬季水母并没有什么异常，而且往往体型更大——尽管海洋专家表示，今年“它们的巨大体型”令人“难以置信”</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 12:35:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-03/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-unusually-large-jellyfish-wash-up-on-israels-shores-after-spate-of-rain/0000018e-03cf-def2-a98e-cfff35c00000</guid></item></channel></rss>